snippet.title: 一◇1◇
snippet.description:
1◇ Indie Game For The Xbox 360. All Video's Are Made by me without adding commentary with the intent on helping someone through a tough spot in the game or for mere entertainment. I hope my videos can help you get out of a tough spot.

Remember If you like what you see subscribe and Like. Feel free to leave comments as I read all of them and enjoy your guy's and gal's input. 

Hopefully you will enjoy any future episodes as well.  Thank you.
